{
  "stem": "2350.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we-- we came through the whole day running to a place where there was a big magazine-- an empty building.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The night was done.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had the two Polacks with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we kept together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I says, let's stay over the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Russians came in at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they took over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we closed this place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Russians start knocking on the door, and they wanted to tear apart the door to see who it is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we opened the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- this was a magazine from shoes or something, so there was a shelf on top.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we all-- girls-- went upstairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Slovakian woman started speaking to them in Russian, that we are from a concentration camp, liberated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they wanted to take the-- everybody says, this is my husband.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Polacks-- they wanted to kill the Polacks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- we screamed so much, and we cried so much, that one Russian says, oh, leave them alone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they walked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the next day, a Russian came to me, and he started talking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going to give you shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he bent down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He touched my feet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm going to give you sugar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm going to come to you 12 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I says, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were screaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were talking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says he's going to get some more rations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was so drunk that he fell in a ditch, and he fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it came like 10, 12 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We say that it's no way to stay here, because we're going to be-- you know, the Russians, they're wild, wild animals.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the [INAUDIBLE] Cossacks or whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
